title: Brendan Schaub Responds, Fresh & Fit Guest Calls In To Expose Them - Off The Rails #35
description: Today we have a very intense call with someone who had a personal run-in with Myron from Fresh & Fit, full of many twists and turns. We also go over the latest developments in the ongoing Brendan Schaub/Bobby Lee saga, and much more!
